lead_paragraph: Germany's Nico Rosberg romped to his fifth win in a row for Mercedes on Sunday and ended Formula One champion team mate Lewis Hamilton's hopes of a third successive Bahrain Grand Prix victory.

headline.print_headline: Rosberg Romps to Fifth Win in a Row
